## 10. Nexus_Scroll         – VirtualScroll (Row-Rendering fuer Posts)
## 11. Nexus_Panels        – Feed / Profile / Settings (Feed → Posts)
## 12. Nexus_PostUI        – Create-Post-Panel
## 13. Nexus_BetaDashboard – Telemetrie Dashboard
## 14. Nexus_TestDriver    – Unit Test Runner

